(110, 1, '2023-03-15 01:45:48', '2023-03-15 01:45:48', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 id=\"article_sapo\"><strong>Bt c qu c no cng nn s hu t nht mt chic o khoc vi tut trong t  ma xun.</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khng ngoa khi ni rng o khoc vi tut chnh l kiu o mi qu c cn s hu trong t  xun h 2023. Nh nhng nhng vn  m p, thanh lch nhng vn ht sc sang trng,  l nhng cm gic m kiu o v cng n tnh ny mang li cho phi p.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Di y l mt s gi  phi  vi o khoc tut ph hp vi bn gi trong mi hon cnh:</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Ha n hong cng s vi s mi v chn vy mini</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>B i s mi v chn vy mini vn  qu c u i ni cng s, nay c thm s tr gip ca o khoc vi tut chng khc no h mc thm cnh. Cch mix  tuy n gin nhng mang li s nn n tuyt i cho cc qu c ni lm vic, ng thi to cm gic m p trong nhng ngy xun se lnh ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-14/Mac-dep-voi-chiec-ao-khoac-sang-chanh-nhat-mua-xuan-1-1678760333-736-width650height652.jpg\" alt=\"Mc p vi chic o khoc sang chnh nht ma xun - 1\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-14/Mac-dep-voi-chiec-ao-khoac-sang-chanh-nhat-mua-xuan-2-1678760333-905-width650height663.jpg\" alt=\"Mc p vi chic o khoc sang chnh nht ma xun - 2\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>o khoc vi tut kt hp cng s mi v chn vy mini gip n cng s trng thanh lch hn vi phn</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Tr trung xung ph vi qun jeans</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Qun jeans v o khoc vi tut thot nhin c v khng h lin quan, song khi ng cng nhau trong mt set  li hp nhau n l. L do l bi o khoc vi tut thng em n v ngoi trng thnh, c phn gi dn trong khi qun jeans li tr trung, phng khong. Hai item tng khng tng thch v tnh b tr cho nhau mt cch hon ho, xng ng l set  c phi p din xung ph ngy cui tun.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-14/Mac-dep-voi-chiec-ao-khoac-sang-chanh-nhat-mua-xuan-3-1678760333-93-width650height766.jpg\" alt=\"Mc p vi chic o khoc sang chnh nht ma xun - 3\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-14/Mac-dep-voi-chiec-ao-khoac-sang-chanh-nhat-mua-xuan-4-1678760333-745-width650height764.jpg\" alt=\"Mc p vi chic o khoc sang chnh nht ma xun - 4\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Qun jeans gip o khoc vi tut bt i vi phn gi dn</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Ti gin m sang chnh vi vy lin thn</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nu nhng cng thc phi  trn i lc khin bn lng tng v phi cn ti ba item  hon thin th cng thc ny li v cng ti gin, cc k ph hp vi nhng ngi bn rn. Ch cn mt chic vy lin thn yu thch, khoc thm o vi tut bn ngoi, mu sc c th tng ng hoc i lp, vy l bn  c th i lm, i hn h sau khi mang thm mt i giy cao gt v chic ti xch hp vi tng th.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-14/Mac-dep-voi-chiec-ao-khoac-sang-chanh-nhat-mua-xuan-5-1678760333-83-width650height632.jpg\" alt=\"Mc p vi chic o khoc sang chnh nht ma xun - 5\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-14/Mac-dep-voi-chiec-ao-khoac-sang-chanh-nhat-mua-xuan-6-1678760333-585-width650height742.jpg\" alt=\"Mc p vi chic o khoc sang chnh nht ma xun - 6\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Him c cng thc phi  no li ti gin nhng mang li hiu qu th gic cao nh vy lin v o khoc tut</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>n gian chiu cao vi chn vy/qun di</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>S tht l nhiu ch em s hu vc dng thp b khng my chung o khoc vi tut. H s rng  dy dn v phom dng hi cng cp ca item ny khin mnh trng nh b nut ngi. Nu cng ang c cng ni s y, bn c th gii quyt trong nhy mt, bng cch nh la th gic ngi i din khi kt hp o tut vi chn vy c  di qu gi hoc qun di qua mt c chn. Kho lo che chn c th mi nhon vi nhng mn  d tm d phi y, khng ai c th nhn ra chiu cao thc s ca bn na ri! Tt nhin, ng qun mt i giy c gt tht cao  n gian thm vi centimet cho mnh nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-14/Mac-dep-voi-chiec-ao-khoac-sang-chanh-nhat-mua-xuan-7-1678760333-582-width650height728.jpg\" alt=\"Mc p vi chic o khoc sang chnh nht ma xun - 7\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-14/Mac-dep-voi-chiec-ao-khoac-sang-chanh-nhat-mua-xuan-8-1678760333-965-width650height655.jpg\" alt=\"Mc p vi chic o khoc sang chnh nht ma xun - 8\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Qun v chn vy cng di khi mix cng o khoc vi tut gip bn gi n gian c kha kh chiu cao</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Mc p vi chic o khoc sang chnh nht ma xun', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-03-15 01:45:48', '2023-03-15 01:45:48', '', 1, 'http://localhost:84/demo/wordpress/?p=110', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(111, 1, '2023-03-15 01:48:24', '2023-03-15 01:48:24', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 id=\"article_sapo\"><strong>Vic mc nhiu lp c th kh vi nhiu ngi nhng d hn nu bn bit cc quy tc sau y.</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>o s mi v qun jean. V d nh o&nbsp;henley qun&nbsp;chinos, nu tri thc s lnh, c th bn cng s khoc thm o khoc. Khi thc hin ng cch, phi nhiu lp c ngha l bn s trng p nht ng thi vn linh hot trong trng hp thi tit thay i.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ma ny, hy th lm theo bn bc sau  thnh cng trong vic xp lp trang phc:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1. Cc loi vi v hoa vn mng hn s c mc&nbsp;trc</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2. Mu ti hn  bn ngoi</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3. Khng qu ba lp c th nhn thy</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>4. Mi lp u c mt mc ch ring, khng ln ln, ln xn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Vi mng hn i trc</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ni chung, bn mun mc cc loi vi nh hn/mng hn gn c th hn v cc loi vi nng hn/dy hn ra xa hn. iu ny c xu hng xy ra mt cch t nhin, nhng bn vn nn ghi nh. iu ny phc v c mc ch thm m v thc t. Vic tho b cc lp nng hn t bn ngoi s d dng hn khi thi tit m ln.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-09/4-Quy-tac-de-thanh-thao-Layering-1-1678352715-208-width480height320.jpg\" alt=\"4 quy tc phi  theo lp chun mc, bn khng nn b qua - 1\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Mu ti hn  bn ngoi</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hu ht cc trang phc nhiu lp s bao gm nhiu mu sc. Bn nn gi cc lp bn ngoi ti hn cc lp bn trong. Bn c th  nghe ni rng mu en v mu m hn s gim bo trong khi mu trng v mu sng hn c tc dng ngc li. Vng,  l s tht v c th c s dng  to li th cho chng ta.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-09/4-Quy-tac-de-thanh-thao-Layering-2-1678352715-30-width480height320.jpg\" alt=\"4 quy tc phi  theo lp chun mc, bn khng nn b qua - 2\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mc nhng mu ti nht  bn ngoi s gip lm thon gn v ko di dng ngi ca bn, c bit nu bn ang mc qun ti mu.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hy ghi nh, y l mt trong nhng nguyn tc yu nht c trong b ny v hon ton c th b b qua. Mt chic o khoc ngoi mu lc  bn ngoi mt b trang phc ton mu en l mt la chn tuyt vi  ph v quy tc ny. Nhng, khi nghi ng, bn khng th sai lm khi tun theo nguyn tc ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Khng qu ba lp c th nhn thy</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bn nn trnh kiu dng cng knh v nhi bng qu mc ny. Gi cho n n gin: 2 lp th d, 3 lp c th th v, 4 lp tr ln c th phc tp, v vy hy cn thn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-09/4-Quy-tac-de-thanh-thao-Layering-3-1678352715-708-width480height320.jpg\" alt=\"4 quy tc phi  theo lp chun mc, bn khng nn b qua - 3\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Mi lp nn c tc dng ring</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cui cng nhng khng km phn quan trng, mi lp cn phi hot ng c lp. Quy tc ny s lm hoc ph v trang phc ca bn. im chnh ca vic phn lp l c th tch lp khi nhit  thay i; v vy c th ni, b trang phc cn phi hot ng  mi lp.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-09/4-Quy-tac-de-thanh-thao-Layering-4-1678352715-11-width480height480.jpg\" alt=\"4 quy tc phi  theo lp chun mc, bn khng nn b qua - 4\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>iu ny c ngha l bn khng nn&nbsp;mc chic o s mi qu rng di o khoc ngoi. Bi v trn thc t, bn ch hi nhn thy chic o ny! m bo rng cc lp ring l ph hp vi phn cn li ca trang phc v v ngoi ca bn s thu ht&nbsp;hn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '4 quy tc phi  theo lp chun mc, bn khng nn b qua', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '4-quy-tac-phoi-do-theo-lop-chuan-muc-ban-khong-nen-bo-qua', '', '', '2023-03-15 01:48:24', '2023-03-15 01:48:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost:84/demo/wordpress/?p=111', 0, 'post', '', 0),
