(114, 1, '2023-03-15 01:50:20', '2023-03-15 01:50:20', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 id=\"article_sapo\"><strong>T l l tt c mi th khi mc mt b vest v s va vn chnh xc l iu cn thit.</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mc vest cn mt s quy tc hi khin cng: Tay o khoc ca bn nn chm vo xng c tay ca bn. Tht lng ca bn phi hi tht li v bn c th nht va nm tay vo gia o khoc v o s mi  ci khuy trn cng.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>By gi chng ta  gii quyt vn  mc  b sao cho phng khong hn. Di&nbsp;y l mt s cch  mc vest mt cch ngu hng:</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Vi o phng</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Phong cch T-Shirt-with-suit l ri ro nht nhng c nhiu phn thng nht. Thc hin phong cch ny v bn s trng tht snh iu. Chn mt chic o phng cht lng cao tng phn vi mu o vest ca bn. Kt hp phong cch ny vi giy th thao hoc giy li v n gin  nhn mnh phong cch casual ca trang phc ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-09/Lam-the-nao-de-mac-mot-vest-theo-phong-cach-casual-1-1678352348-100-width600height600.jpg\" alt=\"Lm th no  mc b vest nam theo phong cch i thng? - 1\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Vi mt chic o Polo</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mc mt chic o s mi polo vi mt b vest l mt b suit casual d nhn hn nh s hin din ca c o. i vi b vest, hy m bo rng o polo ca bn gn gng v khng cht. Chn mu o polo c   tng phn vi b vest ca bn. Bn cng mun la chn giy dng i thng kiu casual, lu  khng thu ht qu nhiu s ch  vo giy dp ca bn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-09/Lam-the-nao-de-mac-mot-vest-theo-phong-cach-casual-2-1678352348-903-width491height600.jpg\" alt=\"Lm th no  mc b vest nam theo phong cch i thng? - 2\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Vi mt chic o s mi hng ngy</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nu bn ch th nghim phong cch&nbsp;casual, hy bt u vi mt trong nhng chic o s mi hng ngy.  l mt b trang phc hon ho cc k linh hot.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-09/Lam-the-nao-de-mac-mot-vest-theo-phong-cach-casual-3-1678352348-746-width512height425.jpg\" alt=\"Lm th no  mc b vest nam theo phong cch i thng? - 3\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Vi o hoodie hoc o thun cotton</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nu bn mun c s tng phn mnh m gia trang phc thng ngy v trang phc chnh t, hy mc o hoodie hoc o chui u bng vi bng v mc vest cng vi n. y l mt ng thi phong cch to bo. Ch cn mc phong cch  vi s t tin. Bn c th mix n vi&nbsp;giy th thao trng rt hay v cht chi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2023/images/2023-03-09/Lam-the-nao-de-mac-mot-vest-theo-phong-cach-casual-4-1678352348-661-width325height406.jpg\" alt=\"Lm th no  mc b vest nam theo phong cch i thng? - 4\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'Lm th no  mc b vest nam theo phong cch i thng?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lam-the-nao-de-mac-bo-vest-nam-theo-phong-cach-doi-thuong', '', '', '2023-03-15 01:50:20', '2023-03-15 01:50:20', '', 0, 'http://localhost:84/demo/wordpress/?p=114', 0, 'post', '', 0),
